VASSAL.build.module

Interface PluginsLoader.PluginElement

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    BshPlugin, ModuleExtension, ModulePlugin, Plugin
    Enclosing class:
    PluginsLoader

    public static interface PluginsLoader.PluginElement
    Any components that are added to the module by a Plugin MUST implement PluginElement to prevent them being written to the buildFile when saving the module. Implemented by Plugin and ModuleExtension.
